msgid "Captain of %{name} states:"
msgstr "%{name} 的队长表示："

msgid ""
"\"I will accept your surrender and grant you and your troops safe passage "
"for the price of %{price} gold.\""
msgstr ""
"「我接受你的投降。支付 %{price} 金币后，你和部队就能安全离开。」"

